Package: oc-module-manage
Version: 1.0.1
Section: development
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Essential: no
Depends: php-cli (>= 7.4), php-json
Maintainer: Gregory Biter <gregorybiter@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/GregoryBiter/oc-module-manage
Description: OpenCart Module Management Tool
 A PHP command-line tool for managing OpenCart modules.
 Available as 'ocm' command after installation.
 .
 Features:
  - Create new OpenCart modules from templates
  - Install and remove modules
  - Development mode with file watching
  - Build modules for distribution
  - Template-based module generation
